      "raw_text": "The American Federation of Labor,\nNo. 1924, at its meeting Saturday\nnight passed resolution which calls\nfor the arrest of every contractor\nemploying men to do city work work\ning over hours day. 1t is under\nstood that men doing work for the\ncity have been working Q hours and a\ndiligent warfare will be waged against\nsuch until the workingmen get down\nto the schedule of 8 hours."
